<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Porzana_parva_(50).jpg" class="image"></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Porzana_parva_(50).jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
Adult male</div>
</div>
